		<title>照顧老年寵物要特別細心！這「五個重點」需時刻提醒自己 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/18/%e7%85%a7%e9%a1%a7%e8%80%81%e5%b9%b4%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e8%a6%81%e7%89%b9%e5%88%a5%e7%b4%b0%e5%bf%83%ef%bc%81%e9%80%99%e3%80%8c%e4%ba%94%e5%80%8b%e9%87%8d%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%8d%e9%9c%80%e6%99%82%e5%88%bb/</link>
		
