		<title>收容所小貓求領養出新招？兩隻貓咪隔籠牽手融化網友的心 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/18/%e6%94%b6%e5%ae%b9%e6%89%80%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e6%b1%82%e9%a0%98%e9%a4%8a%e5%87%ba%e6%96%b0%e6%8b%9b%ef%bc%9f%e5%85%a9%e9%9a%bb%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e9%9a%94%e7%b1%a0%e7%89%bd%e6%89%8b%e8%9e%8d%e5%8c%96/</link>
		
