		<title>寵物真的能「預測天氣」？這3大舉動就是牠的關鍵暗號 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/18/%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e7%9c%9f%e7%9a%84%e8%83%bd%e3%80%8c%e9%a0%90%e6%b8%ac%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%a3%e3%80%8d%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%993%e5%a4%a7%e8%88%89%e5%8b%95%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e7%89%a0%e7%9a%84%e9%97%9c%e9%8d%b5/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 18 Sep 2025 01:36:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[天氣]]></category>
